text: Club Deportivo Victoria is a Spanish football team based in Tazacorte, in the autonomous community of Canary Islands. Founded in 1954, it plays in Preferente de Tenerife, holding home games at Estadio Municipal de Tazacorte, with a capacity of 5,000 seats. ==Season to season== {| |valign="top" width=0%| {|
